cs <- c(0.6, 0.3, 0.0)
K <- 3
s <- NormalSampler2(n = 100,
                    L = 1000,
                    K = 3,
                    prop.outlier = 0.05,
                    cs = cs)
finalSimuValiation(s,
                   method.K = K,
                   lambda.lfmmridge = 1e0,
                   exp.rep = 3,
                   gif = TRUE,
                   comp.exp = FALSE,
                   fast.only = TRUE)

From 1000 genomes simulation

peut d’outlier

cs <- c(0.6, 0.3, 0.0)
K <- 4
G.file <- "~/Projects/Data2016_2017/1000Genomes/Phase3Chrm22/European_Chrm22.rds"
s <- FromTrueSampler(G.file = G.file,
                     n = NULL,
                     L = 10000,
                     K = K,
                     prop.outlier = 0.05,
                     rho = NULL,
                     cs = cs,
                     round = FALSE)
finalSimuValiation(s,
                   method.K = K,
                   lambda.lfmmridge = 1e-1,
                   exp.rep = 5,
                   gif = FALSE,
                   comp.exp = FALSE, 
                   fast.only = TRUE)
